  "text": "We apply a rigorous evaluation metric for the localization of OD and macula, based on which we determine sensitivity in a stringent manner. Previously, [CITATION_1] used this measure for OD localization, by normalizing the mean error. We express the accuracy of localization in terms of normalized error for each image:",
